				<h2><a href="https://applemac.tweakblogs.net/blog/1606/macbook-mini-apples-netbook.html">MacBook Mini - Apple&#039;s Netbook?</a></h2>
				<p class="author">
					Door <a href="https://tweakers.net/gallery/90063/" rel="nofollow">JottemJ</a> op maandag 30 maart 2009 10:14 - <a href="https://applemac.tweakblogs.net/blog/1606/macbook-mini-apples-netbook.html#reacties">Reacties (20)</a><br>Categorie: <a href="https://applemac.tweakblogs.net/blog/cat/661">Mac hardware</a>, Views: 8.459
				</p>
				<div class="article">Eerder schreef ik al over de <a href="https://applemac.tweakblogs.net/blog/1579/apple-3g-netbook.html" rel="external">3G Netbook</a> van Apple en de geruchtenstroom over Apple's kleinste (mobiele) telg blijft maar doorgaan. <br><br> <a href="https://applemac.tweakblogs.net/blog/1606/macbook-mini-apples-netbook.html#more">Lees verder &raquo;</a></div>
